{"tid":203432,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有情緒問題入黎分享下","createTime":"2017-04-16T09:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T23:25:59.000Z","uid":50013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b5344d7f90b0dd382899370202f23a35074b18dd","tid":203432,"uid":50013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:46:34.000Z","msg":"講下我自已先，細佬喺兩年前確診有燥鬱症<br />\n因為屋企出現問題引致壓力過大而導致燥鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而當時又正值dse 時期，但真係冇心情去考，所以除中文一科外都abs。<br />\n每日都淨係鎖自己喺房，望住個窗口。有輕生念頭同自殘傾向。有冇唔開心唔如意就會不停用指甲刮自己，刮到手腳頸都甩哂皮見血。<br />\n後來自知唔到路經社工轉介睇心理醫生，食左一年藥後自己停藥（因為睇心理醫生好貴，又唔想洗屋企咁多錢）<br />\n後來搬左出黎住之後情況有好轉，可能係壓力細左掛。同有人肯聽我傾訴真係會好啲。到宜家自殘嘅情況已經冇左，係間唔中念野會有啲負面不過好快就平復到。<br />\n<br />\n如果你地有咩唔開心不妨講出黎分享下，話唔定會輕鬆啲呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2db1bab924ccc3afe9dd64f06120ad281b31621","tid":203432,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:48:59.000Z","msg":"最後點 點解有錢出黎住<br />\ndse full cert都無點算"},{"pid":"de5678b90a044d18f9673b9b0232d578479eb65d","tid":203432,"uid":50013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後點 點解有錢出黎住<br />\ndse full cert都無點算</blockquote><br />\n我將我返pt儲落儲落嘅錢拎左去比兩押一上，之後都冇繼續讀書開始返full time"},{"pid":"a07650ad5162d60e5891328c0a19901334434f37","tid":203432,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T09:54:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最後點 點解有錢出黎住<br />\ndse full cert都無點算</blockquote><br />\n我將我返pt儲落儲落嘅錢拎左去比兩押一上，之後都冇繼續讀書開始返full time</blockquote><br />\n自己比錢租樓?幾錢租<br />\n你full cert都無有咩工返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a38458376809d52955fe90e04164f410a1afab1","tid":203432,"uid":50013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:00:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最後點 點解有錢出黎住<br />\ndse full cert都無點算</blockquote><br />\n我將我返pt儲落儲落嘅錢拎左去比兩押一上，之後都冇繼續讀書開始返full time</blockquote><br />\n自己比錢租樓?幾錢租<br />\n你full cert都無有咩工返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n租套房，4700租<br />\n做c?l sales"},{"pid":"f02fd4a2e343083d9a38820b49a19f8358eb2036","tid":203432,"uid":50013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T12:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e5d5ce23f73d4bb942fe9f7816cbb4b909b0aa","tid":203432,"uid":70007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T12:53:34.000Z","msg":"有depression <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無人會幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d641342f4328ad8f40e3f85db88c3d6f1d28e019","tid":203432,"uid":50013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有depression <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無人會幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾時開始架"},{"pid":"3d92d64c1dda0dcdcbb3297c2c6d701fedd70800","tid":203432,"uid":50013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有depression <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無人會幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如講下你嘅故事啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0ec3a920b3f10e6656f1b5f16d9621e5da3275","tid":203432,"uid":14093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:07:10.000Z","msg":"躁鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b7fa0bbb83478fa97731ee4d06a6ece2f1aa77","tid":203432,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:22:30.000Z","msg":"冇你地咁嚴重 但由中學開始已經會有情緒突然爆發既問題<br />\n最近一年比較嚴重<br />\n中四既時候已經試過𠝹手同大脾<br />\n上年就因為同男朋友一啲事觸發左<br />\n成個月都冇乜食野 試過喺街暈左<br />\n每日一起身就係負面情緒<br />\n不停喊 咬到自己瘀晒 𠝹手 好想死 但唔想掉低屋企人<br />\n夜晚訓唔著 早醒 去到返工都完全集中唔到 會中途入廁所喊<br />\n之後去睇心理醫生 有keep覆診一排<br />\n後來間唔中都會爆發 但會盡量控制<br />\n因為睇醫生好貴 同唔想朋友擔心"},{"pid":"162a791c0a5ee517eb66247bc7a0adf6c526a9bc","tid":203432,"uid":50013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:22:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>躁鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明咩感覺，就算有睇醫生食藥都冇咩用<br />\n反而會好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa483a8d7e141dccf157fdb32b02fecc5d5b26f7","tid":203432,"uid":50013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T13:25:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇你地咁嚴重 但由中學開始已經會有情緒突然爆發既問題<br />\n最近一年比較嚴重<br />\n中四既時候已經試過𠝹手同大脾<br />\n上年就因為同男朋友一啲事觸發左<br />\n成個月都冇乜食野 試過喺街暈左<br />\n每日一起身就係負面情緒<br />\n不停喊 咬到自己瘀晒 𠝹手 好想死 但唔想掉低屋企人<br />\n夜晚訓唔著 早醒 去到返工都完全集中唔到 會中途入廁所喊<br />\n之後去睇心理醫生 有keep覆診一排<br />\n後來間唔中都會爆發 但會盡量控制<br />\n因為睇醫生好貴 同唔想朋友擔心</blockquote><br />\n睇醫生真係好貴，等公立又唔知等幾耐。<br />\n但你有冇咩興趣試下向多啲呢方面發展睇下會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5396085acd988e74e7c66ab63fc56da58ba188","tid":203432,"uid":14093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T16:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>躁鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明咩感覺，就算有睇醫生食藥都冇咩用<br />\n反而會好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時巴打有無拍拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時都覺得有而個病搞到另一伴好辛苦"},{"pid":"db9194dcef36187eb85729891386a888fa17543f","tid":203432,"uid":30053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:03:28.000Z","msg":"半康復者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家加油 覺得接受自己嘅病好重要<br />\n唔好用正常人個套套落自己度 迫自己要好似普通人咁<br />\n俾啲空間自己 同自己講唔緊要㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多啲讚自己 無差落去已經好叻㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家成日同自己講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都因為得自己先明自己所以先更加要學識接受自己安慰自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755ed985f7237099a9601d5d0a60eec6c13d1f1b","tid":203432,"uid":30053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:05:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>躁鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明咩感覺，就算有睇醫生食藥都冇咩用<br />\n反而會好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時巴打有無拍拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時都覺得有而個病搞到另一伴好辛苦</blockquote><br />\nAgger <br />\n好驚佢覺得煩"},{"pid":"eba762dcebb3ceab5ffda038352c235a3ec3537e","tid":203432,"uid":50013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T23:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>躁鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明咩感覺，就算有睇醫生食藥都冇咩用<br />\n反而會好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時巴打有無拍拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時都覺得有而個病搞到另一伴好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n有呀，其實都算係佢救返我。比好多鼓勵我"}]}